        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 20 at 3:42PM CDT until September 20 at 4:30PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 342 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 8 miles north of
Slapout, or 13 miles west of Laverne, moving northeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

Locations impacted include...
Gate and Knowles.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
